---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import graderIllustration from "../../assets/sidebar-image.webp";

const focusAreas = [
  "Billing efficiency",
  "Patient scheduling and onboarding",
  "Patient experience and care quality",
  "Practice growth and reputation management",
  "Wellbeing and burnout",
];
---

<section class="w-full bg-tebra-hero-bg">
  <div class="mx-auto flex min-h-[calc(100dvh-var(--nav-product-tour-offset))] max-w-[1280px] flex-col justify-between gap-10 px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 sm:py-10 md:px-8 md:py-12 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:gap-16 lg:px-12 lg:py-14 xl:px-16">
    <div class="w-full max-w-[660px]">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.12] tracking-tight text-tebra-teal-dark sm:text-5xl lg:text-[4rem]">
        Assess your practice efficiency with our automation quiz
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 sm:mt-8 sm:text-xl">
        Does the software your practice runs on make life easier or harder for you and your patients?
      </p>

      <p class="mt-5 max-w-[620px] text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 sm:mt-6 sm:text-xl">
        The following 10 questions measure the efficiency and automation across your practice relative to your peers - and what you can do to improve things. Find out how you're performing across areas like:
      </p>

      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-base leading-snug text-gray-600 sm:mt-7 sm:space-y-4 sm:text-lg lg:text-xl">
        {focusAreas.map((item) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-tebra-orange text-tebra-orange" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 12 10" fill="none">
                <path d="M1 5l3.5 3.5L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>{item}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <button
        type="button"
        class="mt-9 inline-flex rounded-full bg-btn-primary px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-btn-primary-hover focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-tebra-teal-dark"
      >
        Evaluate your practice now
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full max-w-[460px] shrink-0 self-end lg:max-w-[520px]">
      <Image
        src={graderIllustration}
        alt=""
        role="presentation"
        class="h-auto w-full object-contain"
        widths={[320, 480, 640, 800]}
        sizes="(max-width: 1023px) 80vw, 34vw"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
